metadata.name: 1SHOS Founder Edition
metadata.description:
1SHOS is a collection of 10,000 unique AI shoes NFTs.

Our vision is to create the largest AI decentralized brand that is created and owned by 1shos community, transcending reality and human imagination.

1SHOS would serve as your community membership cards to join the incoming co-branded mystical projects and draw your own AI shoes in the future.
